103
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:38,870
<i>And they had written very famous books.</i>

104
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:41,500
<i>Murasaki Shikibu wrote "Tales of Genji."</i>

105
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:45,750
I didn't think I could come to school again.

106
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:48,470
Sei Shonagon hadn't written anything

107
