110
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:03,920
That tells us what kind of writers they were.

111
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:10,330
<i>Things go along as usual without me.</i>

112
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:18,070
Okay, this is it for today.

113
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:23,950
<i>- Let's go eat pancakes.<br>- pancakes? Okay.</i>

114
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:42,180
- How about this?<br>- I want more normal clothes.

115
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:44,860
Normal clothes...

116
00:09:44,860 --> 00:09:48,330
I don't know too much about women's clothes.

117
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:54,570
Then...

118
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:59,070
- How about this?<br><i>- It's not cute.</i>

119
