123
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:27,080
Hmm?

124
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,670
Gross.

125
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,650
It's so good!

126
00:10:55,650 --> 00:10:58,460
Don't get my uniform dirty.

127
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,550
Being small is nice at a time like this.

128
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:03,910
