I'm sorry.

137
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:32,640
Eat quickly. It's gonna melt.

138
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,500
Ah.

139
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:36,090
Hmm?

140
00:11:49,970 --> 00:11:52,260
One-inch princess.

141
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:56,170
<i>- One-inch princess?<br>- Yeah.</i>

142
00:11:56,170 --> 00:11:59,950
<i>It is an old legend in this region.</i>

143
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:05,400
<i>It is a story about a cute princess who is small like one-inch boy.</i>

144
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:09,280
<i>A small princess? I wanto to see her!</i>

145
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:13,490
<i>But in the end, she became big again,</i>

146
00:12:13,490 --> 00:12:18,840
<i>got married and had many children.</i>

147
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:22,040
<i>And she became people's protective god.</i>

148
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:25,260
<i>How did she become big?</i>

149
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:28,050
<i>She became big by shaking the lucky mallet stolen from an ogre</i>

150
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:31,860
<i>on a night of a full moon.</i>

151
00:12:32,610 --> 00:12:35,840
A lucky mallet.

152
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,710
Eh?

153
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:42,130
Well... No, no, no.

154
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:49,780
Ah, Minami-kun.

155
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:52,850
What are you doing here?

156
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:56,750
You left school in a hurry, but

157
00:12:56,750 --> 00:13:00,000
