158
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:03,210
You are kind of cute.

159
00:13:03,210 --> 00:13:05,790
I have no choice. I have to get in there.

160
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:08,060
Hmm?

161
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:11,970
May I have a bite?

162
00:13:14,410 --> 00:13:15,880
Cold.

163
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:18,130
Nomura! Sorry.

164
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:20,340
I'm in a hurry.

165
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:23,770
Hey, wait!

166
00:13:23,770 --> 00:13:26,430
What's with him?

167
00:13:26,430 --> 00:13:28,560
Sayori-chan!

168
00:13:28,580 --> 00:13:30,770
You scared me. You disappeared so suddenly.

169
00:13:30,770 --> 00:13:32,040
Masaya...

170
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,420
What's with your face?

171
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:34,690
Nothing.

172
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:37,880
- Sorry. You wanted to eat this?<br>- No.

173
