202
00:18:11,940 --> 00:18:13,110
Hmm?

203
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,960
Eh?

204
00:18:16,610 --> 00:18:18,630
What?

205
00:18:24,550 --> 00:18:26,600
Didn't work.

206
00:18:26,630 --> 00:18:30,500
No way. It was shining.

207
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:35,510
It really looked like it was gonna work.

208
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:41,090
